import { Box, Button, Flex, FormControl, Input, Stack } from "@chakra-ui/react";

export function LoginForm() {
  return (
    <>
      <Flex></Flex>
      <Box padding='25px'>
        <FormControl isRequired>
          <Input placeholder="email" />
          <Input
            placeholder="password"
            type="password"
          />
          <Button
            width='full'
            mt={4}
            colorScheme='blue'
            size="md">
            Acessar
          </Button>
        </FormControl>
      </Box>
    </>
  )
}
